00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:05.000
 How to configure APN automatically on iPhone? 

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:07.000
 Enter the "Settings" menu 

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:13.000
 Scroll down and select "General" 

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:20.000
 Scroll down and select "Network" 

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:26.000
 Turn on 3G Services and cellular data 

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:31.000
 Enable "Browse while roaming" 

00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:34.000
 Click "General" to return to the previous screen 

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:39.000
 Select "About" 

00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:45.000
 Wait a few seconds for the message to appear and click Update 

00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:50.000
 Check the operator line "registered" HOT mobile 12.1 " 

00:00:50.500 --> 00:00:53.000
 Select "General" to return to the previous screen 

00:00:53.500 --> 00:00:56.000
 Select "Settings" to return to the previous screen 

00:00:56.500 --> 00:00:59.000
 Press the Home button to return to the Home screen 

00:00:59.500 --> 00:01:03.000
 Automatic setup failed? Try setting up manually 

00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:04.000
 Enter the "Settings" menu 

00:01:04.500 --> 00:01:09.000
 Scroll down and select "General" 

00:01:09.500 --> 00:01:16.000
 Scroll down and select "Network" 

00:01:16.500 --> 00:01:22.000
 Turn on 3G Services and cellular data 

00:01:22.500 --> 00:01:28.000
 Enable "Browse while roaming" 

00:01:28.500 --> 00:01:36.000
 Select "Cellular data network" 

00:01:36.500 --> 00:01:41.000
 In the "Cellular data" area, click the APN line 

00:01:41.500 --> 00:01:51.000
 Enter the following text: "net.hotm" 

00:01:51.500 --> 00:02:01.000
 In the Multimedia Messages area, click the APN line and enter the following text: 

00:02:01.500 --> 00:02:12.000
 "Mms.hotm" 

00:02:12.500 --> 00:02:21.000
 Scroll down and press the MMSC line 

00:02:21.500 --> 00:02:55.000
 Enter the following text: http://mms.hotmobile.co.il 

00:02:55.500 --> 00:02:59.000
 In the "Internet Sharing" area, click the APN line and enter the following text: 

00:02:59.500 --> 00:03:14.000
 pc.hotm 

00:03:14.500 --> 00:03:17.000
 To return to the previous screen press "Network" 

00:03:17.500 --> 00:03:22.000
 To return to the previous screen click "General" 

00:03:22.500 --> 00:03:25.000
 To return to the previous screen click "Settings" 

00:03:25.500 --> 00:03:30.500
 To return to the home screen, press the "Home" 

